document_data.Relationships:
{{fq
|text= Percival is Cadderly’s friend. Perhaps Cadderly’s closest friend.
|source=[[Danica Maupoissant]]
}}
The small creature enjoyed the company of Cadderly, as well as the cacasa nuts, butter and acorns the young priest would feed him.

Cadderly's bond to Percival became so strong that the priest gained abilities of the creature, and could even sprout white squirrel limbs to climb and leap across terrain, which a human would usually find impossible to traverse, with ease and speed.
